---

<Layout title="About Our Ministry | Divine Connection">
  <Navbar />
  
  <main class="flex-1 w-full">
    <section class="relative h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDEF6F2psbf58a_oyDQdQwEdF9YOV_Z7htVGu6Zn3Wya5I7YcYaCAupdja4wOybHutmHJ3sX10ec4c7j0KI3ucdQ_s1oyd_NaJNaqx06At12Y88jjH6FoJMUTV6mWhltgawJ2iDN_anSJ8fDMWnFYPB1_Q5gD--IAKSABLJKXW7is84IEbbArudsUaiEmqc23r3SEZ0TRqfPy6Bb64Ph5ySY37VDJnnG_B-JhmkwApRz0ZuL1mqZcUE4wrGok8EJIbYp0zsFOvv5p0')] bg-cover bg-center">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-[1px]"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/30 via-white/50 to-white"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-6 max-w-4xl">
        <span class="text-gradient font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6 block opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up">Our Legacy & Mission</span>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-6xl md:text-8xl font-light italic leading-tight mb-8 text-slate-900 opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up delay-100">About Our Ministry</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 font-light leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up delay-200">
          A community dedicated to spiritual growth, authentic connection, and radical love in the heart of Suitland.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce opacity-50 text-slate-400">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">keyboard_double_arrow_down</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 px-6 relative overflow-hidden bg-white">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-600/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] -z-10"></div>
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="relative group">
            <div class="parallax-bg aspect-[4/5] rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl glow-accent" style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuB59U-gyWmMHPymWdiaH_Pxhhb3wxdKRE9Ng3W3CXJYnNkXhgitIF4FbjS3SpkEOEXc26ikPjWBkyEcNaGdKNZtufu8NRxAs4KEF1nuqBo-uW6oGxaQzUPU9ZX29A3EGAfqi9yKvWh3p5bhjP8oEmySW3x1PXobtyFMXSaE_S1uZ4vYV5oQpuATovHEU1agO3xAEj_VVV8nHWLWQuesRXjrFJkwx4g2tyQ5thaZv77Pu_wA-ywzgpRnusZlrZw6ymDE90CEx-Vb1rc');">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-purple-600/5 mix-blend-overlay"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -right-8 w-64 aspect-square rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border-8 border-white hidden md:block shadow-lg">
              <img alt="Founding years" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCptrK8Yqd0TVMr3rkCFXhjkH-Y_CKlgKTUwdLZcbGJKmjNW_007-dyIIMcQgoGTcl6kyZPeOL05VqoVCC2oGnjtZ28G4LG3BfkIYjeUCVH9cdaiKK6AUvwQOCUKO9zwTiAAvDIwJ7Si8Lk9iSnj3EM8GOA8uMxlK04OmhRGmYT8cy0zh9oXMv7ShR1-2UOGzt7qCEhg5cWilGBN5YRYEfPQZ-WfClY686I1DmlSHC2J530KW7nwkJWm9GXO2aAkdeJjnm8MbLrie4"/>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium italic text-slate-900">Our Story</h2>
            <div class="space-y-6 text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed font-light">
              <p>Founded over three decades ago, Grace Community began as a small gathering of faithful individuals in a living room in Suitland. Our vision was simple: to create a space where everyone, regardless of their background, could experience the transformative power of faith.</p>
              <p>Today, we have grown into a vibrant family. While our building has changed, our heartbeat remains the same. We are committed to being a lighthouse for our community, providing hope and tangible support through our diverse ministries.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-4">
              <button class="group flex items-center gap-3 text-gradient font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">
                Read more about our journey 
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform text-purple-600">arrow_right_alt</span>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-slate-50 border-y border-slate-100">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium italic mb-6 text-slate-900">Leadership</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Meet the dedicated team serving our congregation and guiding our vision forward with humility and purpose.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div class="group relative h-[400px] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAG85QWAVWaGQqy_hBonbFmppB4-BipzLqjr8qJRvMFxOlkRtYpXc-x60IILWRMx7EdpspF0qwSuAts-uQFHIRs2399byncjKUDFaeQEW9hdlZIrxpzv4DPxjw_4nm4xKfg4zfw9vbFXZ4BkCPrg82ZLfm5Z1TxgP3WOqRNcIT57YK3lkWysceNSORqKxrXWGfBpz1RF30toECF_l4J_uuqBSR_4yV2EF95kdB3OJBVP74j1S-0Metf0VKE-Qqu2Eq_eGiDptG08Fw');"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/90 via-slate-900/20 to-transparent opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-6 text-center transform translate-y-2 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-medium italic text-white mb-1">Rev. David Mitchell</h3>
              <p class="text-purple-300 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Lead Pastor</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group relative h-[400px] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCSIphywLq5xfppO1c9M_s6QgNoWQ7-5is79nIAVNBwIyRYRXasOkGTybVDU7SthannfpRfK-vw8srJVsQyY1cUzV17V-yBLCgZYsCx2FWvsQa0XeYEXj7Yn2-qoeAWOpznZ81arSQXwByJlLajXGuVG24GLzpmXuiRUPmPCpSftuWgj6KdOwoTxfGtft6AnoSOs6y2_TnI3cUtBwMnyJTTVrUT0VyWmXDxpMCwBOl5ke86eNJWimKJdxLBUPxaPFYgFxLoNsIZf7U');"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/90 via-slate-900/20 to-transparent opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-6 text-center transform translate-y-2 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-medium italic text-white mb-1">Sarah Jenkins</h3>
              <p class="text-purple-300 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Executive Pastor</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group relative h-[400px] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDd5eDrgAntTlkLMYXJmwfDHtuztaocmFY5FhKXXq8WRsFwkhcd3Yn1eE_RJohKH1lVqVbR9TFclk5e2sjnrAu9WToMEDrPkLo-0sg71_xvxzxFXlLHA4P-IZEFKCo3_--OKaUGy1HxoVF1yY94TWDvjzpqFGXG7yybT7H2cEiSVA-30iu2lZQdWx0yLKSsfG6G7upVAJ-J9z3f0UnS73xyWj6nwvWuRY6wGUOB8oFYk-maD03IgDSaX4NENCnOi1bEO8E20iUEoKY');"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/90 via-slate-900/20 to-transparent opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-6 text-center transform translate-y-2 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-medium italic text-white mb-1">Marcus Thorne</h3>
              <p class="text-purple-300 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Worship Director</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group relative h-[400px] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAqAuWyghwoEAdDTFbpkLFBo6IknX2Om4cp4LlUCCRhNxVEPw31mBYe8tceOTrT0Dc-R1ZfevXAu1BKfEQOln_lOh3o9HW3OSFwwCzCZbtKmqSZpLoYBc1rUfxsc94BVKqGcp7-Z02-alQnv4IoqeDpdd444DYmlbBkA--ZWP53cynjILzSCJZCAM3bVYVdQoAbZ4dpmOpjYJLne3aAofcTZzYYsOb2eM8NivSHRSxXZkF_8YfOyRM_S6txPdXG7k4O8IHcoF0CLto');"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/90 via-slate-900/20 to-transparent opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-6 text-center transform translate-y-2 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-medium italic text-white mb-1">Elena Rodriguez</h3>
              <p class="text-purple-300 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Youth Ministry</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 px-6 relative overflow-hidden bg-white">
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-slate-200 to-transparent"></div>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium italic mb-6 text-slate-900">What We Believe</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-500">Our core values and the theological pillars that guide our teaching and service.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <details class="group glass-card rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border-slate-100" open>
            <summary class="p-8 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl italic font-medium text-slate-800">The Power of Community</h3>
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180 text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600 text-purple-600">expand_more</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-8 pb-8 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-light">
              We believe that spiritual growth happens best in circles, not just rows. Our life groups and community outreach are centered on the idea that we were never meant to walk this path alone. Together, we find strength, accountability, and joy.
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="group glass-card rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border-slate-100">
            <summary class="p-8 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl italic font-medium text-slate-800">Scriptural Foundation</h3>
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180 text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600 text-purple-600">expand_more</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-8 pb-8 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-light">
              Every teaching and initiative at Grace Community is rooted in the Word. We strive to interpret ancient wisdom for modern living, ensuring our faith remains active and relevant in today's world.
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="group glass-card rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border-slate-100">
            <summary class="p-8 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl italic font-medium text-slate-800">Radical Hospitality</h3>
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180 text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600 text-purple-600">expand_more</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-8 pb-8 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-light">
              Following the example of Christ, we open our doors wide. No matter your history, doubts, or background, there is a seat at the table for you here. We celebrate diversity as a reflection of God's creativity.
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="group glass-card rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border-slate-100">
            <summary class="p-8 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl italic font-medium text-slate-800">Global and Local Impact</h3>
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180 text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600 text-purple-600">expand_more</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-8 pb-8 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-light">
              Our mission extends beyond the walls of our sanctuary. From feeding the hungry in Suitland to supporting global missions, we believe faith is proven through service and sacrificial love.
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="glass-card rounded-[3rem] p-12 md:p-20 text-center relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-purple-600/5 via-transparent to-blue-600/5"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-6xl font-medium italic mb-8 text-slate-900">Ready to join our family?</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 font-light">
              Whether you're visiting for a Sunday or looking for a place to call home, we'd love to meet you.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
              <button class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600 text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl font-bold hover:scale-105 transition-transform shadow-xl shadow-purple-600/20">
                Plan Your Visit
              </button>
              <button class="bg-white border border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl font-bold transition-all shadow-sm">
                Contact Us
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .parallax-bg {
      background-attachment: fixed;
      background-position: center;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: cover;
  }
  .glow-accent {
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px -10px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15);
  }
  .glass-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }
  .text-gradient {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #9333ea, #2563eb);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }
    
  details > summary {
      list-style: none;
  }
  details > summary::-webkit-details-marker {
      display: none;
  }
</style>
